{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 111, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "smcn", "body": "This is the penultimate boss of Naxxramas, and can only be fought once all 4 wings are cleared. More information can be found at http://www.wowwiki.com/Sapphiron.", "date": "2006-09-12T19:40:30-05:00", "rating": 57, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 1, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "this boss has 3,000,000hp", "creationdate": "2008-07-08T21:23:01-05:00", "id": 340893, "rating": 1, "commentid": 111, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "inusnoozer", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Not for long. Patch 3.3 will allow players to use teleportation orbs to travel back and forth from Sapphiron's Lair.", "creationdate": "2009-12-02T09:44:19-06:00", "id": 432985, "rating": 7, "commentid": 111, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "121812", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The correct term is [url=http://www.wowwiki.com/Soon]Soon[/url]", "creationdate": "2010-01-25T07:35:25-06:00", "id": 145193, "rating": 21, "commentid": 111, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "GinjaNinja", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Not so sure if that's correct. I went into Naxx during the Love Is In The Air world event, and pitied the Love Fool that I dropped. Got bored so I decided to go into the Frostwyrm Lair, and at first I didn't see anything. I went further and noticed a bunch of bones and a skull on the ground, when they started floating and spinning in the air, and then Sapphirion appeared.", "creationdate": "2010-02-27T05:23:42-06:00", "id": 443440, "rating": -1, "commentid": 111, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "232757", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Sapphiron can be engaged prior to killing any other bosses.", "creationdate": "2010-03-01T22:09:36-06:00", "id": 443717, "rating": 1, "commentid": 111, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Wooticus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2425, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "913", "body": "Some of the items not listed on Sapphiron:\n\nThe Restrained Essence of Sapphiron\nhttp://www.wowhead.com/?item=23046\n\nClaw of the Frost Wyrm\nhttp://www.wowhead.com/?item=23242\n\nSapphiron's Left Eye\nhttp://www.wowhead.com/?item=23049", "date": "2006-10-30T21:30:01-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 4476, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "3118", "body": "The basic premise is FrR and LoS. Hands down, he has the coolest spawn graphic in the game.  \r\n\r\nHe drops a ton of loot.  Enchants, items, ego.", "date": "2006-11-25T20:06:17-06:00", "rating": 59, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Not true. If you are pressed up against the ice block you will not get hit. Did this on 25-man yesterday. There are some locations where the ice block DOES NOT PROTECT YOU though. The grace area behind the ice block is not very forgiving but there is some leeway to it. Be as close as you can and stack up.", "creationdate": "2009-01-20T08:36:49-06:00", "id": 381979, "rating": 1, "commentid": 4476, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "102269", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Correction: LONGEST spawn in the game.", "creationdate": "2009-09-23T19:07:22-05:00", "id": 425837, "rating": 5, "commentid": 4476, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "8inchunbuffed", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I'd take his spawn timer over Poseidus'. :p", "creationdate": "2014-08-06T16:12:29-05:00", "id": 762888, "rating": 1, "commentid": 4476, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Alfa", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
