{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 330857, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "79477", "body": "Spamming Renew as a priest at level 70 is incredibly effective here. Up to 10 targets can be Renewed at once (though mana is an issue if you cast that often), doing slightly less healing than the Aura does on those 10 people. I'd guess a single Druid would be able to keep 10 people up with Rejuv spam and fairly high +heals. Pre-HoTing should not be underestimated in this fight.", "date": "2008-07-20T04:26:42-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
