{"commentv2": 1, "number": 12, "id": 344185, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "kt0rse", "body": "The single most coolest (pun not intended) boss in Naxxramas instance.\r\n\r\nAs it seems, the ice blocks behind which you have to hide from his devastating ability, the Frost Breath, is a bit bugged. So to be completely sure that you are in the right position when he casts Frost Breath try attacking him from behind the ice block, if it says \"Target not in the line of sight.\" then you are safe. Other than that, stay out of the Blizzards and use your mana rationally and you should be fine.", "date": "2008-08-04T09:44:57-05:00", "rating": 14, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "or you can just run to the wall and stay there, you wont die ;)", "creationdate": "2009-04-09T17:37:35-05:00", "id": 398747, "rating": -1, "commentid": 344185, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "347468", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
