{"commentv2": 1, "number": 31, "id": 513352, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "279910", "body": "16 wipes yesterday.. this is [b]NOT[/b] cake. we were two healers, restoration shaman and holy paladin.\r\nIf you want to do this with only two healers, please take a restoration druid with you. It is important to have persons to focus on the curses. Restoration druids have HoT's and decurse. These are two of the most important spells at this boss.", "date": "2008-12-16T06:15:58-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 32, "id": 514124, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "280962", "body": "My answer to why people have very different experiences with this encounter (feel free to disagree)---\r\n\r\nBottom line: sometimes his aura does tick every second, other times it does not.\r\n\r\nExplanation:\r\nSapphiron's frost aura does not act the same from raid to raid.  It could be a recent hot fix or just bad luck or maybe it could vary within the encounter.\r\n\r\nThe first few times my guild fought this guy, we downed him no problem.  In a recent attempt, we wiped numerous times.  In looking at combat logs, here is what I found from the easier previous nights' combat logs:\r\n\r\nTime 0:00 Hit by frost aura.\r\nTime 0:01 Frost aura is refreshed.\r\nTime 0:02 Hit by frost aura.\r\nTime 0:03 Frost aura is refreshed.\r\n..etc\r\n\r\nThus, the aura was hitting every two seconds.\r\n\r\n\r\nIn the recent failed tries:\r\n\r\nTime 0:00 Hit by frost aura.\r\nTime 0:01 Hit by frost aura.\r\nTime 0:02 Hit by frost aura.\r\nTime 0:03 Hit by frost aura.\r\nTime 0:03.2 Frost aura is refreshed.\r\nTime 0:04 Hit by frost aura.\r\n\r\nHere, it is hitting every second.\r\n\r\nNote, I simplified the combat text to make it easy to understand and also note that there is some variety within each log, but this is generally what I saw.\r\n\r\nConclusion: if you are getting hit every second, might need 3 healers or some FR gear, or a great strategy with two healers.  Good luck!", "date": "2008-12-16T14:00:20-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
