{"commentv2": 1, "number": 37, "id": 526942, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "287739", "body": "Yep.  The above statement.....\n\n[quote]No, he is no longer immune to frost spells or abilities, nor is he resistant to it. Frost DKs and mages have no problem anymore.[/quote]\n\n...is utterly and completely false.  \n\nWhile not immune, he is indeed highly resistant to frost spells....  just a short wws parse quote...\n\n[quote]21:10'46.719\tMalkinorr Frostbolt hits Sapphiron for 5112 Frost. (Critical) (539 Resisted)\n21:10'49.656\tMalkinorr Frostbolt was fully resisted by Sapphiron.\n21:10'57.188\tMalkinorr Frostbolt hits Sapphiron for 3222 Frost. (Critical) (1358 Resisted)\n21:10'59.922\tMalkinorr Frostbolt hits Sapphiron for 3860 Frost. (Critical) (1084 Resisted)\n21:11'04.359\tMalkinorr Frostbolt hits Sapphiron for 4404 Frost. (Critical) (795 Resisted)\n21:11'07.438\tMalkinorr Frostbolt misses Sapphiron.\n21:11'09.438\tMalkinorr Frostbolt hits Sapphiron for 1920 Frost. (1079 Resisted)[/quote]\n\nNot hit capped - so it included a miss - there were quite a few FULL resists, and [b]all[/b] were at [i]least[/i] partially resisted.\n\nPlease downrank it into oblivion.", "date": "2008-12-23T15:22:15-06:00", "rating": 89, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Easily soloable now. No tactic required. I ran in circles to avoid the cold rain, but even that is optional.", "creationdate": "2013-01-07T01:54:56-06:00", "id": 620075, "rating": -7, "commentid": 526942, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "438040", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-12-23T15:27:00-06:00", 1, "287739"]}
