{"commentv2": 1, "number": 42, "id": 547454, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Serai", "body": "by far the most annoying thing on this fight is the frost aura that deals 12k dps to a 10man raid at all times\r\n\r\nsince sapphirons enrage timer is very easy your racing against your healers mana bar, with potions now only useable once per fight your going to run out sometime\r\n\r\nfor dpsers the main priority is to avoid the blizzards as suddenly taking high dmg drains a healers mana far faster than a predictable stream of dmg", "date": "2009-01-05T02:02:30-06:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I think you meant to say 1.2k dps to raid at all times, 12k dps is a wipe 100% of the time", "creationdate": "2009-01-14T05:08:14-06:00", "id": 380392, "rating": 0, "commentid": 547454, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "302350", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 43, "id": 548408, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "275496", "body": "I don't se what everyones problem for this boss is... our guild casually raids 10 man Naxx every week as we are actually a PvP guild, however first time we raided Naxx we reached Saph, wiped twice and then downed him on the 3rd try, our average gear level was heroic rares and epics/crafted epics, i really dont see how people are struggling, if you healers are going oom, either your dps is seriously lacking and thye arent getting him down anywhere near in time or your healers have SERIOUS problems with their mana pool / mp5, our general setup is resto druid, holy priest and 1 random healer depending on who else is online and we have no problems at all, after the first time weve run Naxx about aother 4-5 times and we've one shotted him every time no problems.", "date": "2009-01-05T15:34:01-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
