{"commentv2": 1, "number": 62, "id": 612564, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Barrney", "body": "Anyone else notice how Sapphiron is one of the few (or only) blue dragons (or formerly...) who's name doesn't end in -gos or -gosa?\nie. Maly[b]gos[/b], Sindra[b]gosa[/b]", "date": "2009-02-17T03:24:39-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I noticed that as well, but his name is SAPPHIRon. Sapphire is a blue crystal, the same way snow is thought of as \"a light blue crystalized form of water\", that might be the reason, considering he is a blue dragon, and his \"superpower\" is frost/ice/snow =D", "creationdate": "2009-03-29T06:23:07-05:00", "id": 396736, "rating": 0, "commentid": 612564, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "RetributionHamma", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-02-17T12:53:33-06:00", 1, "Barrney"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 63, "id": 614443, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "273450", "body": "did his aura got a nerf in 3.0.8, just one-shoted him with no FRR gear, and we wiped alot pre 3.0.8 even WITH the gear.\r\n\r\nbut its a very fun fight for a healer.", "date": "2009-02-18T13:48:14-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 64, "id": 618073, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "237816", "body": "This fight really plays well into a bear tank's specialties. While other tanks can have problems hitting 540 def in a lot of Fr gear, but druids maintain uncrittability from just talents. on top of the the Fr gear has huge amounts of stamina, which scales incredibly well with druids due to bear form and all the stamina increasing talents.\r\n\r\nI've found that i can tank in 4 pieces of frost resist (chest, belt, boots, ring) gemmed pure stamina gems and still dont have to worry about DPS hitting the threat ceiling. With this amount of frost resist, improved leader of the pack, and proper use of cooldowns such as barkskin, frenzied regen, etc. The healers could mostly neglect me and worry about the DPS. a resto druid rolling 3xLB and a rejuv was enough to keep me alive between air phases, meaning he could largely ignore more for the nine seconds between refreshing his hots, allowing him to focus more on tossing spot regrowths, Lifeblooms and wildgrowths.\r\n\r\nThe other big help we had was we agreed everyone must get behind the same iceblock. This way the priest and druid could spam wild growth and circle of healing to get everyone topped off in preperation for the ground phase.\r\n\r\nthose two little pieces were key in us downing sapph our first time, as well as making sure your dps understands the blizzard mechanics and moves quickly. Obviously once you get used to the mechanics and your gear catches up to the encounter, the tank can start subbing out some of his Fr gear and stuff like that.", "date": "2009-02-21T13:04:23-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 65, "id": 619633, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "309638", "body": "Frost resistance gear IS essential to taking him down untill you have a group thats exceptionally well geared, smart enough to stay out of blizzards, and skilled healers. \r\n\r\nTanks should NOT wear frost resist, as heals will be focusing on them anyway, and most likely adding a piece or 2 of frost resist will drop them below the def cap, which is bad.\r\n\r\nEveryone except the MT should have at least 2 pieces of frost resist gear, this fight is not a dps race, it is an endurance fight, there is no intelligent reason not to wear frost resist unless your going for the 300 club achievement.\r\n\r\nThere is a more [url=http://www.worldofstrats.com/Sapphiron/tabid/125/Default.aspx]in-depth guide here[/url] that helps a lot with the strategy of this fight.", "date": "2009-02-22T17:08:33-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 66, "id": 621972, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "328643", "body": "Looks like Mage/Druid Curse Removal are good for dealing with Sapph's Life Drain - is there confirmation available as to whether Cloak Of Shadows/Ice Block, etc. will work?", "date": "2009-02-24T14:35:50-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 67, "id": 622598, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "328981", "body": "Hi\r\n\r\nYesterday we were doing 10 man nax. And we were at saphiron. I was off tank. And somehow main tank dies. Then the boss took a dps (\u0131 was on battle stance). Quickly switch to defensive stance and hit taunt. Guess what happens: did not work. Then \u0131 wait for 8 secs (cooldown) hit again did work also. wait another 8 secs push taunt again did not happen. After 5-6 taunts we got wipe. cause boss never attacked me. I did not use challenging shout because it did not come to my mind. Anyhow what is for taunt?\r\n\r\nSome saying he is immune to taunt. Is it true?", "date": "2009-02-25T03:57:24-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Depends on what message you got.  If he's Immune, you'll see \"Immune\" in front of him when you taunt.  Otherwise if it didn't work you'll get \"Resist.\"  As far as I know,  Sapphiron is immune to taunt in both 10 and 25-man Naxx.", "creationdate": "2009-02-25T10:59:24-06:00", "id": 82367, "rating": 2, "commentid": 622598, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "328643", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
