{"commentv2": 1, "number": 80, "id": 694204, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Atzemis", "body": "As of 3.1, it appears that running to the edges of the room will no longer protect you from his deep breath. I learned this the hard way unfortunately...", "date": "2009-04-26T01:55:52-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "yep...its darn stupid healers are out of range on u and u die so fast", "creationdate": "2009-04-28T12:29:56-05:00", "id": 402792, "rating": 0, "commentid": 694204, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "hackandmore", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Dont blame the healers for you running out of range.... If a DPS ever blames me for getting out of range it annoys me so much -.-", "creationdate": "2009-07-31T06:56:04-05:00", "id": 417993, "rating": 0, "commentid": 694204, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Abbot", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "i was refering to a dps running out of range and making them stupid...healers are uber :))", "creationdate": "2009-08-14T05:03:51-05:00", "id": 420411, "rating": 0, "commentid": 694204, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "hackandmore", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
