{"commentv2": 1, "number": 82, "id": 747824, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Vreyara", "body": "[quote]finally downed him yesterday.\r\n\r\ntanks: warr, druid <he was dpsing in cat on this fight>\r\nhealers: me <disc priest, specced for this fight only - actually i might stay in it>, holy pally, resto shaman\r\n5 dps: 2x rogue, shadowpriest <who died by not hiding behind blocks on 1st sapphiron's flight...no replenishment/hp from IVE>, hunter, dk\r\n\r\neasy fight. [b]pally would decurse[/b], also had FR aura. We've made our dps to wear some FR equip if they had it, but none on healers and tank. Also my SR prayer helped on missed decurses ;-)\r\n\r\ni really dunno how we could be wiping on him a day before soo many times. possibly, being a bit spread when he shoots icebolts is the biggest deal. and ofc hiding behind blocks they leave. didn't even use shadowfiend and i ended at ~20%, although u have to count in improved wisdom, mp5 flask and mana totems. had over 500 mp5 while casting[/quote]\r\n\r\nQuite interesting, I didn't know Paladins could remove curses.", "date": "2009-06-15T17:08:46-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
