{"commentv2": 1, "number": 87, "id": 788091, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "344122", "body": "In a recent patch Sapphiron's aggro range was drastically reduced, and you can now stand right outside the inner circle Sapphiron stands in.", "date": "2009-07-25T07:24:11-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 88, "id": 789926, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "KyorraWindblade", "body": "Priests, rejoice!\n\nHoly priests can survive the Deep Breath every 3 minutes, if they screw up / ice block too far away, by casting Guardian Spirit on themselves. It removes the buff, and you're on 50% Health instead of dying.\n\nShadow Priests -may- survive the effect, if they have some decent Stamina. The Frost Breath isn't an instant kill effect, it deals 112500 to 187500 Frost damage (average 150000). Dispersion reduces damage by 90%, meaning it only deals 10% damage: 11250-18750, average 15000. PW: Shield calculates after mitigation, so if we have a Shield up before we Disperse, we have a retardedly high effective health, and we're saved easily. \n\nIf not...  Well. You weren't supposed to, anyway.\n\nEDIT: Calculation about shield - Thanks Abbot.", "date": "2009-07-27T06:10:38-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Shield absorbtion is calculated after any mitigating effects, such as armour or dispersion. So if you pop a 3k shield right before dispersion, with shiled will end up absoring 30k damage before you being to take anything - easy win =]  edit: typo", "creationdate": "2009-07-31T06:58:05-05:00", "id": 112880, "rating": 4, "commentid": 789926, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Abbot", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-02-02T02:49:48-06:00", 2, "KyorraWindblade"]}
