{"commentv2": 1, "number": 93, "id": 863226, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "93865", "body": "I was able to tank Sapphiron-25 tonight without getting behind the iceblocks. I Divine Shielded the first one, Ardent Defender'd the second, then stacked Divine Protection with gylphed Hand of Salvation on myself. With three self-contained cooldowns, I never needed to escape the frost breath, and was able to eat it in its entirety.\r\n\r\nAestu, Bleeding Hollow-US", "date": "2009-10-09T22:36:18-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
