{"commentv2": 1, "number": 110, "id": 1624440, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "ClancyF", "body": "I soloed him last summer. Hunter 4.2. I tried many nights of trying over 6 months finally got him down in 10 man. Recorded it. Showed how to do. 372i at the time i think. I haven't lasted more then a few seconds in 25man so far. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rIq9vYp_beo", "date": "2012-02-10T07:01:43-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 111, "id": 1630443, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "813024", "body": "Soloed the [b]25 man[/b] version as a blood dk, 31/8/2 lichborne tanking spec with 2/2 abomination's might using pure dps gear, ilvl 382. No buffs, food, pots or flasks were used. Would have been easier with a more dps-oriented spec and some buffs.\r\n\r\nIncoming damage is not an issue. Death strike easily outheals his damage. The enrage timer is going to be pretty tight because he has ~13 million hp and you have 15 minutes, so you need to do 14.4k dps. You actually need about 15-16k dps as he will heal himself with lifedrain throughout the fight. In dps gear I am hit capped with 25 expertise, I would not have done enough dps with anything less. Army, DRW & ghoul on the pull. Army will come off cooldown 10 minutes into the fight, but I saved it until the end because I knew it was going to be close. I ended up doing 15.4k dps and he enraged with about 200k hp left. I popped army again seconds before enrage and burned him down. \r\n\r\n\r\nDrops slightly more gold than 10 man and the heroic key to focusing iris.", "date": "2012-02-22T17:50:13-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 112, "id": 1632894, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Esploratore", "body": "Soloed the 10 men version as a very bad geared (just made a dk as my warrior sucks at soloing) blood dk with 336 item level.\r\n\r\nFull dps gear, I don't understand why getting enrage problems with tank gear when I, with my fail item level, killed him in 8 minutes, so 7 left till enrage.\r\n\r\nI always rotated around him to avoid blizzard (thanks, nobbel, for the soloing video as a protection paladin, the one in which he enraged and you died at the same time of the boss), and was almost always at 100% hp, sometimes I went down to 85%, but while iceblocked I get the time to use vampiric blood (glyphed) and blood tap to bring me back to full.\r\n\r\nWas an interesting fight, but will be much more interesting trying the 25 version with good item level; I did a bit more than 4 millions in 8 minutes, so can probably do 8 millions of his 12 millions hp at 25 within the enrage.\r\n\r\nHere's some screenshots of the fight, mostly for hp reasons, doesn't go low at all as bad geared dk.\r\n\r\nhttp://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/443/sapphironstart.jpg/\r\nhttp://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/341/sapphiron2962.jpg/\r\nhttp://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/542/sapphiron2170.jpg/\r\nhttp://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/848/sapphiron1256.jpg/\r\nhttp://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/855/sapphiron716.jpg/\r\nhttp://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/9/sapphiron73.jpg/\r\nhttp://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/201/85dksolosapphiron336.jpg/", "date": "2012-02-28T08:12:01-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 113, "id": 1633788, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Laevar", "body": "Certainly solo-able on 10man as a Protection Warrior using [item=77193 domain=www]\r\n\r\nI'll attempt to do it on 25man after the next reset.\r\n\r\nAny reasonably defensive class should be capable of at least a 10man solo. His melee strength and frost aura are not overly strong and his ice block will always target you in a 1v1, making the frost bomb miss you 100% of the time.\r\n\r\nOf note, the kill time was 8:11 and the zerk timer is 15:00. If you are a low dps class (like a prot warrior) alternate gearing/prep may be required to meet the 25man zerk timer.", "date": "2012-03-01T12:49:16-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 114, "id": 1649753, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Esploratore", "body": "Now at 383 item level, soloed at 25, blood dk in full dps gear, I had to use a 300 strength flask when I did him the first time, beat the enrage by 50 sec; without it I wiped once at 14k, lol.\r\n\r\nAs other have said, despite him hitting a bit harder on 25, as dk it's nothing, it's just a dps race; move out of blizzard, else you will have to use healing cds and lose precious dps time! AMS can also help on this.\r\n\r\nUse dancing rune weapon on CD as well as every other dps cooldown you might have.\r\n\r\nAvoid army of the dead, its damage is almost nothing AND can take away aggro from you, letting you lose important vengeance; can be useful if he enrages at 100k to finish him.\r\n\r\nAt 386 dps item level I can now kill him in around 13 mins without flask.\r\n\r\n---------------------\r\n\r\nAs arms warrior, I 2-man him with a holy paladin (at 25, ofc, 10 player is extremely easy, also soloable for prot warriors), without the dk absorbs I can feel the difference from 10 player, on 10 he hits for 8-10k, on 25 like 16-20k, but definitely healable for the whole duration of the fight (11-12 mins) with around 387-392 item level for both of us. \r\n\r\nAlways running out of blizzard, as taking more damage than necessary is definitely not a good option.\r\n\r\nAlso, when soloing or two-manning, he iceblocks both players on the air phase, so no need to go behind iceblocks, you will be in one.", "date": "2012-04-06T23:38:49-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
