{"commentv2": 1, "number": 120, "id": 1854178, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Morbius", "body": "Soloed the 10 player version as an 85 blood DK in Cataclysm dungeon and rep gear. Strategy is the same for 25 player. Did it in unholy presence because at the time this video was made Glyph of Dark Succor was the best way to heal yourself.\n\nIt's basically a tank and spank. Circle strafe around him to avoid the blizzard. Move away when he flies up. Don't worry about the iceblock. Just run back in when it wears off and continue DPSing him.\n\nHere's the video:\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5iZ7p_9Wo2Y", "date": "2013-05-18T21:29:22-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-05-18T21:34:15-05:00", 2, "Morbius"]}
