{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 3290501, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Shivrael", "body": "I dunno bout the rest of you guys, but this was a disappointing plug for what was once one of the most epic introductions to a boss in the game. \r\n\r\nIn its prime, the Sapphiron fight was a legendary encounter beginning with a subtle twitch of bones assembling on the floor of a vaulting necropolis penthouse suite. \r\n\r\nNow it's just Kel'Thuzad playing Ding Dong Ditch with us for a quest line. Nyeh. Nyeh.", "date": "2021-01-14T10:13:32-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}